@{
    
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}



<style>
   
    /* Style the tab content */
    .tabcontent {
        float: left;
        padding: 0px 12px;
        border: 0px solid #cadcf6;
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        color: #00408a !important;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    p {
        color: #3c586d;
        line-height: 30px;
    }
    li {
        color: #3c586d !important;
    }
</style>






<main id="content">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="bg-img-hero text-center mb-5 mb-lg-8" style="background-image: url('../Content/img/cookie-policy.jpg');">
        <div class="container space-top-xl-3 py-6 py-xl-0">
            <div class="row justify-content-center py-xl-4">
                <!-- Info -->
                <div class="py-xl-10 py-5">
                    <h1 class="font-size-40 font-size-xs-30 text-white font-weight-bold mb-0">Cookies Policy</h1>
                    <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
                        <ol class="breadcrumb breadcrumb-no-gutter justify-content-center mb-0">
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item font-size-14"><a class="text-white" href="@Data.GetMeRoom.GlobalConstant.ConfigVariables.SITEROOTPATH">Home</a></li>
                            <li class="breadcrumb-item custom-breadcrumb-item font-size-14 text-white active" aria-current="page">Cookies Policy</li>
                        </ol>
                    </nav>
                </div>
                <!-- End Info -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!--End Hero Section -->
    <div class=" terms_tab border-bottom border-color-8 pt-lg-1">

        <div class="container mb-4 mb-lg-11 pb-lg-1">
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                    <div id="cookie" class="tabcontent" style="padding: 25px; min-height: auto; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255) !important; display: block;">

                        <p>At BookMyHotels, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information from misuse. We ensure that all data shared by our Users, Visitors, and Customers is securely managed in accordance with our privacy standards.</p>

                        <p>This Cookie Policy explains how BookMyHotels uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience when searching for cheap hotels, budget stays, or special accommodation deals worldwide.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Use of Cookies</h4>
                        <p>To provide a seamless and secure user experience, BookMyHotels uses cookies and similar technologies that help us personalize your journey, improve website performance, and maintain security across our platform.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">What Are Cookies?</h4>
                        <p>Cookies are small text files placed on your device when you visit our website. These files store information about your browsing behavior and preferences, allowing us to recognize your device during future visits.</p>

                        <p>Cookies help us:</p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Remember your login details so you don’t need to re-enter them repeatedly.</li>
                            <li>Personalize your experience with tailored content and offers.</li>
                            <li>Analyze site traffic and user engagement to improve our services.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p><strong>Please note:</strong> Cookies do not store any sensitive personal information such as passwords or payment details.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Types of Cookies We Use</h4>

                        <h5>1. Strictly Necessary Cookies</h5>
                        <p>These cookies are essential for the proper functioning of the website. They respond to specific actions such as adjusting privacy settings, logging in, or filling out forms. Disabling these cookies may impact website performance or prevent access to certain areas. They do not store any personally identifiable information.</p>

                        <h5 class="mt-3">2. Performance Cookies</h5>
                        <p>These cookies help us analyze website traffic, measure page performance, and understand how visitors interact with our site. The data collected is aggregated and anonymous. If you disable these cookies, we may not be able to track or improve website performance effectively.</p>

                        <h5 class="mt-3">3. Functional Cookies</h5>
                        <p>These cookies enhance website functionality and personalization, often set by us or by third-party hotel partners. Disabling them may affect certain website features or cause parts of the site to function incorrectly.</p>

                        <h5 class="mt-3">4. Targeting Cookies</h5>
                        <p>These cookies are set by advertising partners to deliver relevant advertisements based on your browsing habits and interests. They do not store personal data but identify your browser and device. Disabling them may result in receiving less targeted or generic advertisements.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Updates to This Cookie Policy</h4>
                        <p>BookMyHotels reserves the right to update or amend this Cookie Policy at any time. Updates may be communicated through:</p>

                        <ul>
                            <li>Email notifications</li>
                            <li>Website announcements</li>
                            <li>Posting a revised statement on this page</li>
                        </ul>

                        <p>We encourage all Users and Visitors to review this policy periodically to stay informed of any changes.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Contact Us</h4>
                        <p>For any queries related to data privacy, cookie preferences, or information deletion requests, please contact us through the BookMyHotels website.</p>

                        <p><strong>Note:</strong> Disabling or deleting cookies may limit access to certain features and functionalities on our platform.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Cookie Settings and Analytics</h4>
                        <p>BookMyHotels collects technical data such as browser type, language preference, operating system, and referral URLs. This information helps us improve our services and user experience.</p>

                        <p>We also use Google Analytics and similar services to analyze user behavior and enhance performance. Some of this data may be shared with third-party analytics providers.</p>

                        <p>
                            To opt out of Google tracking, visit:
                            <a href="https://www.google.com/policies/technologies/ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
                                https://www.google.com/policies/technologies/ads/
                            </a>
                        </p>

                        <p>Users may also manage their cookie preferences through their browser’s Cookie Settings.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Social Media Widgets</h4>
                        <p>Our website includes features such as the Facebook Like and Share This buttons, which may collect your IP address and interaction details. These activities are governed by the privacy policies of the respective social media platforms.</p>



                        <h4 class="mt-4">Email Communications</h4>
                        <p>BookMyHotels uses secure third-party email systems to send newsletters, promotional offers, and service updates—only to users who have opted in. These emails may contain identifiers such as “pixel tags” or “clear GIFs” for tracking message engagement and improving content relevance.</p>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

